title: (PSX-PSP) Street Fighter Collection 1 converted properly (Kingdo
description:
STREET FIGHTER COLLECTION 1:

STREET FIGHTER is one the most successful videogame franchises in history. Now you can relive some of that history with STREET FIGHTER COLLECTION. The three games included are: SUPER STREET FIGHTER II, SUPER STREET FIGHTER II TURBO, and STREET FIGHTER ALPHA 2 GOLD. All the games are perfect translations of their arcade counterparts; each fighter retains its moves and combinations, including fireballs and quick throws. When you win the martial arts tournament, you will discover that character's motivation for fighting. If you are a STREET FIGHTER fan, you owe it to yourself to get your hands on STREET FIGHTER COLLECTION.


Disc 1 - Super Street Fighter 2 & Super Street Fighter 2 Turbo

Disc 2 - Street Fighter Alpha 2 Gold

Tested and working on CFW 5.00 M33-4 combined with the 500 popsloader and 3.72 POPS...KloWn
